    <item>
      <title>改革党在选举活动计划中的李</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/reform-party-s-lee-on-election-campaign-plans-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国改革党的总统候选人兼议员李·朱塞克（Lee Jun-Seok）讨论了他的计划，在前总统Yoon Suk-Yeol被宪法法院维持的一项弹each裁决中被正式罢免后，在韩国竞选总统大选。他专门与Shery Ahn在“彭博社：亚洲贸易”上讲话。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/reform-party-s-lee-on-election-campaign-plans-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 01:24:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾第一个托管交易日的前往熊市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/tsmc-slumps-10-on-tariff-woes-as-taiwan-returns-from-holiday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾的股票指数记录在案最多，在假期后恢复了熊市，这使它在熊市的轨道上走上了正轨，并抓住了唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税远足触发的全球抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/tsmc-slumps-10-on-tariff-woes-as-taiwan-returns-from-holiday</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 01:08:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>RBI看到随着全球不确定性的增长，延长了创纪录的现金提升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/rbi-seen-extending-record-cash-boost-as-global-uncertainty-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师说，印度储备银行将把其创纪录的现金注入扩展到银行体系中，因为它阻碍了经济免受全球逆风的加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/rbi-seen-extending-record-cash-boost-as-global-uncertainty-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nintendo Plummets在关税引起的日本股票中的消失10％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/nintendo-plummets-10-in-tariff-induced-wipeout-for-japan-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nintendo Co.和Sony Group Corp.周一在东京下跌了10％以上，这是由于总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对他对美国进口征收的深远关税的最新评论加剧了日本的广泛抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/nintendo-plummets-10-in-tariff-induced-wipeout-for-japan-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 00:58:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>彭博监视04/06/2025</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/bloomberg-surveillance-04-06-2025-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着贸易战争激发衰退的担忧，全球市场受到压力，这加剧了自联盟大流行以来股票最糟糕的一周。彭博监视设置了另一个动荡的一周的舞台，并带有华尔街一些知名人士的洞察力和评论。丽莎·阿布拉莫维奇（Lisa Abramowicz）的乔纳森·费罗（Jonathan Ferro）与从华尔街到华盛顿及其他地区的领导人和决策者进行了交谈。在交易日，没有其他计划可以更好地职位投资者和高管。


 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/bloomberg-surveillance-04-06-2025-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 00:53:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着关税风险触发避风港的竞标，中国的债券激增，减轻了赌注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/china-bonds-surge-as-tariff-risks-trigger-haven-bid-easing-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的政府债券飙升，将基准收益率提高到了记录下最低的，因为投资者担心美国关税和货币宽松的赌注，投资者急忙购买了避风港资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/china-bonds-surge-as-tariff-risks-trigger-haven-bid-easing-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 00:18:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金亿万富翁在鲁特加深时抨击特朗普的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/ackman-calls-trump-tariffs-a-mistake-and-massively-in-excess</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比尔·阿克曼（Bill Ackman）和斯坦利·德鲁肯（Stanley Druckenmiller）谴责唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统决定发起广泛的全球关税，这使市场陷入混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/ackman-calls-trump-tariffs-a-mistake-and-massively-in-excess</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 23:32:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票火山口，国库在关税动荡上集会：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，全球股票的飞行加速了，投资者堆积在避风港资产中，因为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税加深了中国宣布报复措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:40:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>铜的公牛奔跑转向途径，因为关税的现实叮咬的现实</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/copper-s-bull-run-turns-into-a-rout-as-reality-of-tariffs-bites</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两周前，交易员警告说，威胁我们对金属的关税会挤压全球供应，铜价飙升。现在，随着唐纳德·特朗普总统的更广泛的贸易战争使需求的前景更加重要，公牛队正在面对有史以来最严重的抛售之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/copper-s-bull-run-turns-into-a-rout-as-reality-of-tariffs-bites</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 21:31:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
